export const homeOjbOne = {
    lightBg: true,
    primary: false,
    topLine: "A Masters in Electrical and Computer Engineering Student at Northeastern University",
    lightTopLine: false,
    lightText: false,
    lightTextDesc: false,
    headline: "Hi! I'm Chaman Singh.",
    description: "I'm a Machine Learning aficionado who is passionate about unraveling the mysteries of artificial intelligence. Recently, I took the next big step by enrolling in Northeastern University's Masters in Electrical and Computer Engineering program at Boston. Apart from all that time I have been spending on artificial brains, you can find me talking about football (the one the call soccer in the US (⚆_⚆) ), going on hikes or trying my hand in cooking.",
//  I love meeting new people, so please feel free to get in touch!",
    buttonLabel: 'Resume',
    img: require("../images/profile.svg").default,
    alt: "Their should be an image here",
    imgStart: '',
    start: '',
    link: 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1QDzovbCQ68NY4t-LnSUn5Q8xogDlaRbL/view?usp=sharing',
    btn: true,
    lst: false
  };
  
  
  export const homeOjbTwo = {
    lightBg: false,
    primary: false,
    topLine: "What I've been working on.",
    lightTopLine: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    headline: "Recent Projects",
    description: "I have worked on numerous training and inference pipelines such as tumor segmentation, object detection, and GANs. I also have experience deploying them on various types of computing platforms. I have extensively used several Deep Learning libraries and toolkits such as PyTorch and TensorFlow to solve engineering problems involving Computer Vision and Natural Language Processing. ",
    buttonLabel: "SEE MORE OF MY WORK",
    img: false,
    alt: "Their should be an image here",
    imgStart: 'start',
    start: 'true',
    link: 'https://github.com/singhchaman',
    btn: true, 
    lst: true,
    lstType: 'proj'
  };
  
  export const homeOjbThree = {
    lightBg: true,
    primary: false,
    topLine: "Things I have worked on.",
    lightTopLine: false,
    lightText: false,
    lightTextDesc: false,
    headline: "Publications",
    description: "I've had the privilege of contributing to some publications that reflect my passion for research in machine learning, and they serve as a testament to my commitment to advancing understanding in this ever-evolving field.",
    buttonLabel: "Google Scholar",
    img: false,
    alt: "Their should be an image here",
    imgStart: "",
    start: "",
    link: 'https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=F6QHYXAAAAAJ&hl=en',
    btn: true,
    lst: true,
    lstType: 'article'
  };
  
  export const homeOjbFour = {
    lightBg: false,
    primary: false,
    topLine: "I'd love to hear about you :-)",
    lightTopLine: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    headline: "LET'S BE INTERNET FRIENDS",
    description: "If you want to ask me questions about anything or just want to get in touch, feel free to reach out on LinkedIn or drop me an email at singh.ch@northeastern.edu and I will get back to you asap.",
    buttonLabel: "",
    img: false,
    alt: "Their should be an image here",
    imgStart: "start",
    start: "true",
    link: "/events",
    btn: false,

    lstType: 'social'
  };
